Have no idea that I would actually spent new year with these guys ..
Well 2017,
It's definitely a nice opening for you then..
I'm looking forward to lots lots more of surprising memories to come..
Please don't dissapoint us üòÑ

Last year's last post was dedicated to the ones I called family for the last few years.
This year, it was dedicated to these guys who I'd recall as family for another few years to come.
Yes that this picture is kinda blurry and everyone wasn't so ready and everything, but that was the memory that I want to treasure. That we all  came from lots of different places, we are weird and random and noisy and everything, but then our path crossed and here we are finding out that somehow, our hearts belong together.
.
2016,
You are one hell of a harsh year. You lifted me up so high but you burried me alive as well. You weren't easy, but I made it out alive.
A year does make lots of differences. Some people I used to call friends had turned into strangers, and some strangers that came out of nowhere had somehow turned into friends.
The last few weeks have been a struggle, and as 16 will soon find an end, I hope all these struggles will too.
2017,
You are everybody's new hope.
Please be nice to everyone. Maybe you wouldn't be perfect either, but I wish that you'd at least treat us better than 16. I do have expectations to lean on you, and I'm working on to achieve it.

Welcome 17,
We'll greet you in two and a half hours üòä

Smile,
They would be hatin' anyway üòÅ
